        "text": "It is proved that adopting techniques to enhance the in-context retrieval capability of RNNs, including Retrieval-Augmented Generation and adding a single Transformer layer, can elevate RNNs to be capable of solving all polynomial-time solvable problems with CoT, hence closing the representation gap with Transformers."
